  "text": "Lee et al. [CITATION_1] presented a recursive recurrent neural networks with attention modeling (R2AM) for lexicon-free scene text recognition. the model first passes input images through recursive convolutional layers to extract encoded image features I, and then decodes them to output characters by recurrent neural networks with implicitly learned character-level language statistics. Attention-based mechanism performs soft feature selection for better image feature usage.",
